Package: cbloldataR
Type: Package
Title: A Package For Acquiring Data Of CBLOL From Leaguepedia in R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Pedro", "Rocha", email = "pedro.diniz.rocha@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This packages offers a set of functions aimed for harvesting data 
    of CBLOL from Leaguepedia. It was originally created as an exercise for 
    practising web scrapping, data cleaning and package creation. In the end, 
    the functions available here facilitate access to CBLOL stats and, 
    therefore, may help journalists, analysts or enthusiasts to work and 
    visualize data from CBLOL within R. 
